Teresa Graves https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teresa_Graves 0 Teresa Graves (born Terresa Graves; January 10, 1948 – October 10, 2002) was an American actress and singer. As the star of the 1974 Get Christie Love!, Graves is credited as being the first black woman to star in her own hour-long drama television series.
